{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c338775840","title":"中共甘肃省委财贸系统批判右倾机会主义分子张天珩、马树兴简报（第13期）","origin":"根据作者或他的亲属提供的原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b349708ab4","index":0,"year":1959,"month":10,"day":26,"articleId":"c338775840"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bda0bf40bf","type":"title","text":"中共甘肃省委财贸系统批判右倾机会主义分子张天珩、马树兴简报（第13期）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"98972e7722","type":"paragraph","text":"[党内文件 注意保存；财贸系统秘书组　第13期　1959年10月26日]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"3be9b8c5ff","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十六日上午开大会，批判马树兴同志的问题。参加人员除财贸系统科（处）长以上党员干部外，还有财政厅的全体党团员。王国瑞同志首先介绍了马树兴同志反党反社会主义的材料（材料另发），接着马树兴同志进行检讨（材料另发）。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"19c79f438e","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴同志主要检讨了四个问题：一、反对大跃进，反对公社化，二、阶级根源和思想根源，三、思想作风和工作作风，四、对错误的态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"8bea61fe23","type":"paragraph","text":"在反对大跃进，反对公社化方面，他说主要表现在粮食问题上，错误的认为：第一、粮食产量增长不大，有些地区粮食产量是压出来的，订产量时宁高勿低，有些地区产量上不去，就拔白旗，产量是按试验田估算的。第二、征购任务太大，购了过头粮，省上规定征购任务占产量的百分之三点多，实际有的地方是百分之八点多，甚至十点多，群众口粮无保证，购了就销，浪费劳力。第三、认为反瞒产私分是小题大作，零打碎敲，是鸡爪当龙爪，中心问题是产量不高。（王国瑞同志插问：你认为省委这样搞错了吗？马树兴说：我认为搞的过火）。第四、认为有些地区粮食供应过火了，来了个紧刹车，应销的也不销了、是不负责任。第五、去年秋季收割有浪费，吃得多了一些，所以实际粮食少下来了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"ede4122780","type":"paragraph","text":"他认为以上是粮食紧张的主要原因，有些地方没粮吃，死了人，群众不满，伤了感情，因此主张少购少销，希望省委能彻底克服工作中虚夸和浮而不实的作风。（王国瑞：这点省委在整社时已经提出，但和你的要求不同，省委要求在落实的基础上提高，你是一压再压）。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"7e3e6e6f68","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴说：这些问题去年不敢明目张胆的说，今年听了霍维德的两次反党言论，觉得气味相投，就很自然的在粮食问题上和霍维德结合起来了。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"a9d26c2d75","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：恐怕其他问题还有吧。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"7caeac7cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"严万汉：在霍维德讲以前你就讲了。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"bd033abac2","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：我认为粮食问题是政策上的错误，财贸会议上霍维德的讲话是代表省委纠偏的。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"cdbed4d4e5","type":"paragraph","text":"樊希英：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"b62071a20e","type":"paragraph","text":"省委没叫传达，你在财政厅干部会上传达了，想把干部纠到那里去呢？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"cce07cb1b1","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"11e8b3c185","type":"paragraph","text":"想制造干部思想混乱。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"060d525534","type":"paragraph","text":"严万汉：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"cf018bed69","type":"paragraph","text":"你在下面没有经过地方党委，为什么做反宣传？我有一次从天水回来你对我说，现在农村吃不上粮，你粮食厅怎么办？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"7da4961e51","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：我接受霍维德的反党思想。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"cad30759c9","type":"paragraph","text":"樊希英：不能推在霍维德的身上，应找你自己的思想根源。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"9cc7d24dbb","type":"paragraph","text":"赵崇德：有些问题你在霍维德讲前一两个月就讲了，你三番五次的说老百姓要造反，这是什么意思？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"09065f3f00","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：我把已克服和正在克服的缺点进行扩大宣传，这是我对党采取仇恨的态度。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"f2163951a4","type":"paragraph","text":"杨树锦：你为什么是仇恨党？","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"709147e732","type":"paragraph","text":"樊希英：你没有仇恨党的理由，在1939年你被俘时，马锡五专员动员群众救你，谁知你给马专员写来了这样的信。党开除了你的党籍以后又允许你重新入党，你有什么理由仇恨党，你要好好检查思想根源。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"d0b4372453","type":"paragraph","text":"严万汉：53年就反对粮食征购，当时征购五亿斤的指标你提出要减少，在会上没有通过，你说以后看吧，为此还报到西北财政局。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"8651bf0874","type":"paragraph","text":"赵崇德：你说陕北群众造反，能举岀一些例子吗？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"1d80b12086","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：这是听霍维德这样讲的。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"ec613c6f56","type":"paragraph","text":"有人提出，你在通渭说群众把党日塌了是更发挥了霍维德的话。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"4114f2dee5","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：这句话我没有讲，可以查对。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"69d5ced0fd","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：已经查对过了，我们专门派人去了解过了。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"e6176615fb","type":"paragraph","text":"在大炼钢铁和兴修水利方面，马树兴说：认为劳力用得多了，把群众的锅收购了，把房子拆得多了，群众没住的。因此到处喊叫，抓住个别问题，把农村说得—团糟。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"3967a64720","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：你说农村不如过去吗？","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"13f908a1b0","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：不如过去我还没有想过。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"c504209207","type":"paragraph","text":"在检查阶级根源和思想根源时，马树兴说我出身剥削阶级，参加革命后，思想没有彻底改造，1939年环县事变，被俘后，贪生怕死，成为党的叛徒，47年胡宗南进攻延安时，借口料理女儿的婚事及老人有病，请假回家，逾期数月未回机关，就在家和一个姓刘的（也是请假回来未去）到东三县参加游击队工作。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"b5c03c5810","type":"paragraph","text":"翟羽：你是否想投降敌人呢？","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"0e2050c427","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"d30d2ffc5a","type":"paragraph","text":"我当时并没有想投降敌人。我在东三县工作离家近，老人病又重，好照顾家庭。九月间老人病亡，敌人这时也失败了，但我仍推迟到十一月组织上派人去找我时，我才去。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"abc444f48d","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"e148ee6d3b","type":"paragraph","text":"当时组织上不派人去找，你再去不去？","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"d94f1a1c68","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"330b9cd488","type":"paragraph","text":"还是要去的。当时主要想老人刚死，要在家中安置一下。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"4f125487e8","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"b3a1204ef3","type":"paragraph","text":"在环县事变中你投降了敌人，给敌人暴露了些什么问题？","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"453e23b217","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"1ca3c8419d","type":"paragraph","text":"没暴露什么问题。因那时敌人整天和我们打仗，把我们压在后面。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"b7ff5d4490","type":"paragraph","text":"樊希英：","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"82544a7b78","type":"paragraph","text":"你在赵志五（鸣琴）家中住的吗？","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"7b3fa0ae83","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"64efb4aaba","type":"paragraph","text":"你还给人家点火烧烟，怎么能不问你呢？","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"5a69c3a3da","type":"paragraph","text":"翟羽：","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"3f034b0ec6","type":"paragraph","text":"据说你和土匪的小老婆在一起，人家给你打洗脸水哩！","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"0d60f84cb7","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：等敌人返回来时，我们的军队也来了。和赵老五住在一起，是因我们的军队来了，他怕脱不了身，想依靠我维护他全家。他那里写了几次信，开始是他们起草的，我不肯写，他们硬说：“要保护我全家生命呀！”因为我是专署的秘书，有些叛变分子都认识我。","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"a2260c167f","type":"paragraph","text":"赵崇德：","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"f0f7ec32c5","type":"paragraph","text":"叫你自守了吗？","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"d43d6f60ad","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"876a9fc967","type":"paragraph","text":"没有。他们也来不及。敌人把我们逮捕后，敌伪县长只见了一面。当时只听他说是八路军进攻他们的，说你们红军不讲信用，你们占了环县多少地方，我们才占了多少等。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"0207891c46","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"bce58e7607","type":"paragraph","text":"你被俘多少时间？","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"9e8facf76a","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"91f54dcf3b","type":"paragraph","text":"有三、四个月。","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"2b0c3b1b45","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"92e5e8f7df","type":"paragraph","text":"三、四个月那还不问你吗？","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"9bd3232e91","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"a313f3cabc","type":"paragraph","text":"那时常打仗，敌人把我们押到一个寨子里，常不来。那几封信是以后咱们军队包围了才写的。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"9bc43cfd23","type":"paragraph","text":"刘依民：","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"33fbf2a729","type":"paragraph","text":"和你一起被俘的人有的牺牲，有的被打得厉害，你和敌人同吃共眠，你在给马专员的每次信中都说敌人宽待你，敌人为什么这样宽待你呢？","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"9d19b855c9","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"0c7d82bddf","type":"paragraph","text":"我们一起被俘的人没有一个被拷打，只有一个人是被一颗手榴弹炸死的。","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"a38a662ca8","type":"paragraph","text":"刘依民：","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"9960740f07","type":"paragraph","text":"从信中看，你和赵老五的哥哥在一起住过几个月。","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"ad1057d775","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"a3296edb0f","type":"paragraph","text":"那还可调查，看是否住在一块。","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"a4e1845692","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞：","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"69c169dfb7","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人会问你的吧？","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"bfb711270d","type":"paragraph","text":"马树兴：","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"fa261ffed5","type":"paragraph","text":"那时乡长、支书叛变了的很多，敌人情况都了解。","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"855d099d66","type":"paragraph","text":"王国瑞同志最后指出：马树兴同志的检讨还很不深，只戴帽子，无具体事实。特别是对环县事变中的情况还谈的很不深。下午同志们继续揭发和批判。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"},{"id":"b62e98c927","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：中共甘肃省委办公厅印。","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840"}],"page":{"id":"15adfd3115","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"c338775840","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}